---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import KitForm from '../components/KitForm';
---

<Layout
  title="Get a Reflection Card"
  description="Reflection questions for developers - conversation starters and prompts for thinking about your development career and experiences."
>
  <main class="card-page">
    <h1>Get a card?</h1>

    <section class="card-content">
      <p>
        Did you see me (Leaf) at a conference recently, and did you get a "questions for reflection"
        card from me? Or did you see a question posted online?
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm <a href="/">Leaf</a>, and I'm writing a <a href="/book">book</a> about the <em>human</em
        >
        side of being a developer. You can read more of my writing <a href="/posts">here</a>.
      </p>

      <img
        src="/images/posts/2025/cardsStickers-1.jpg"
        alt="Two business cards and a small round sticker. One card says 'Beyond Writing Code Questions for reflection' and 'In what ways might slowing down actually help us to move faster?' The other card has a watercolor and ink drawing of a creature with a thought balloon that just has a question mark. The sticker has the same watercolor creature and the text 'Beyond Writing Code' and 'beyondwritingcode.com' around it."
        class="card-image"
      />

      <p>
        The questions on the cards are all potential questions for reflection in the book! Get draft
        content, hear about book progress, and have the opportunity to have input into the book by
        signing up below:
      </p>

      <KitForm formId="e8bea8d2f2" client:load />

      <p>
        After you confirm, hit reply on the confirmation email and tell me what question you drew.
        Share your thoughts if you like!
      </p>

      <h2>About the cards</h2>

      <p>
        In preparation for meeting a whole bunch of people at{' '}
        <a href="/speaking-at-leaddev-staffplus">LeadDev StaffPlus</a> and the{' '}
        <a href="https://ghc.anitab.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Grace Hopper Celebration
        </a>
        , I wanted something fun to hand out.
      </p>

      <p>Stickers, for sure. I love stickers. That was easy.</p>

      <p>
        But when I saw{' '}
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/benlloydpearson/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Ben Lloyd Pearson
        </a>{' '}
        handing out "affirmations" at the{' '}
        <a href="https://videos.itrevolution.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Enterprise Technology Leadership Summit
        </a>
        , I knew he was onto something.
      </p>

      <p>
        He offered people a deck of small cards, and I chose "Delete the code you don't want to see
        in the world" from the deck. Clever!
      </p>

      <p>
        I considered being a copycat, but I was struggling to come up with more than about three
        affirmations. Once I decided to make it "questions for reflection" instead, wellâ€¦ I thought
        of 50 pretty quickly, enough to make a full set.
      </p>

      <p>And then I thought of another 50.</p>

      <p>
        I ordered two versions: business card size, and sticker size. I used this{' '}
        <a href="https://refer.moo.com/s/leaf4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          moo.com referral link
        </a>{' '}
        if you are interested in checking out their products!
      </p>

      <h2>The full list of questions</h2>

      <p>
        Want to see all the questions? Here's a PDF with all of them! Use them for reflection,
        journaling, or conversation starters.
      </p>

      <div class="pdf-download">
        <a href="/Question-cards-for-conferences-Questions.pdf" class="download-button" download>
          Download Question Cards PDF
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .card-page {
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .card-content {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .card-image {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .pdf-download {
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .download-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: #1e4080;
    color: #fcfaf9;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    transition: background-color 0.2s;
  }

  .download-button:hover {
    background-color: #2a5499;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-accent-teal);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  em {
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
